  "task_html": "<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0ieK90uUmTU\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"video-link-card\" style=\"margin-bottom:16px;\">\n  <div class=\"video-link-icon\">▶</div>\n  <div class=\"video-link-text\">\n    <div class=\"video-link-title\">Übersicht: Längen-, Flächen- und Raummaße</div>\n    <div class=\"video-link-sub\">YouTube: Alle Einheiten im Überblick</div>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"video-link-arrow\">↗</div>\n</a>\n<p style=\"font-size:14px;margin:0 0 14px 0;\"><strong>Ergänze die fehlenden Werte in der Tabelle.</strong></p>\n\n<div class=\"task-block task-green\">\n  <div class=\"task-block-label\">Flächenmaße</div>\n  <div class=\"tbl-wrap\"><table>\n    <thead><tr><th>mm²</th><th>cm²</th><th>dm²</th><th>m²</th><th>km²</th></tr></thead>\n    <tbody>\n      <tr>\n        <td><input class=\"cell-input\" data-ans=\"2500\" placeholder=\"?\"></td>\n        <td class=\"given\">25 cm²</td>\n        <td><input class=\"cell-input\" data-ans=\"0.25\" placeholder=\"?\"></td>\n        <td><input class=\"cell-input\" data-ans=\"0.0025\" placeholder=\"?\"></td>\n        <td><input class=\"cell-input\" data-ans=\"0.0000000025\" placeholder=\"?\"></td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td><input class=\"cell-input\" data-ans=\"720000\" placeholder=\"?\"></td>\n        <td><input class=\"cell-input\" data-ans=\"7200\" placeholder=\"?\"></td>\n        <td><input class=\"cell-input\" data-ans=\"72\" placeholder=\"?\"></td>\n        <td class=\"given\">0,72 m²</td>\n        <td><input class=\"cell-input\" data-ans=\"0.00000072\" placeholder=\"?\"></td>\n      </tr>\n    </tbody>\n  </table></div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"check-bar\">\n  <button class=\"btn-check\" onclick=\"checkEinheitenFlaeche()\">✓ Überprüfen</button>\n  <button class=\"btn-reset\" onclick=\"resetEinheitenFlaeche()\">↺ Zurücksetzen</button>\n  <span class=\"check-result\" id=\"check-result-einheiten-flaeche\"></span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"task-block task-orange\" style=\"margin-top:14px;\">\n  <div class=\"task-block-label\">✏️ Erkläre</div>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:1.7;margin-bottom:8px;\">Erkläre: Warum hat die Umrechnung von cm² → m² den Faktor 1/10.000 (also ÷10.000) – und nicht nur ÷100?</p>\n  <textarea style=\"width:100%;min-height:70px;padding:8px 10px;border:1.5px solid #fed7aa;border-radius:8px;font-size:13px;font-family:inherit;resize:vertical;\" placeholder=\"Deine Erklärung...\"></textarea>\n  <p style=\"font-size:12px;color:var(--ink2);margin-top:6px;\">💡 Male dir ein Quadrat mit Seite 1 m = 100 cm. Wie viele cm² passen da rein?</p>\n</div>",
  "sol_html": "<div class=\"h2-example\" style=\"margin:0;\"><div class=\"h2-example-title\">Lösung</div><div class=\"h2-example-calc\">\n<div class=\"tbl-wrap\"><table>\n  <thead><tr><th>mm²</th><th>cm²</th><th>dm²</th><th>m²</th><th>km²</th></tr></thead>\n  <tbody>\n    <tr><td>2 500</td><td class=\"given\">25</td><td>0,25</td><td>0,0025</td><td>0,0000000025</td></tr>\n    <tr><td>720 000</td><td>7 200</td><td>72</td><td class=\"given\">0,72</td><td>0,00000072</td></tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table></div>\n<p style=\"font-size:13px;margin-top:10px;\">Bei Flächen: jede Stufe = ÷100 &nbsp;(weil Länge² → Faktor wird quadriert)</p>\n</div></div>"
}